                    "value": "<p>The Sihedron surveyor releases a magitech pulse that disrupts nearby tech. All creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:24] save. The Sihedron surveyor can't use Aeon Pulse again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Aeon Pulse]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Creatures and items with the tech trait are @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Glitching]{glitching 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> Creatures and items with the tech trait are @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Glitching]{glitching 3}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but creatures with the tech trait are also @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{slowed 1}.</p>"
